Description: Limestone ostracon: On one side only, five incomplete lines of a duplicate text of the Teaching ofAmenemhat, I-IVa (P. Millingen 1,1-7 = P- Sallier II 10,1-5).
Curator's comments: Published: F. Adrom, Die Lehre des Amenemhet (BAe 19, 2006). Translation of Amenemhat: Parkinson, The Tale of Sinuhe and other Ancient Egyptian Poems 1940-1640 BC (Oxford World's Classics 1999), 203-11.
